"from\": 345, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having gone viral onsocial media, the shooter has seen other athletes, including Swedish pole vaulter Armand Duplantis, celebrate using his now iconic pose.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999944082077854, \"rank\": 3.230867855727807e-06, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viral onsocial media\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"the shooter\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"his now iconic pose\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Dikec, competing in his fifth Games, has now revealed that his calm demeanour did not reflect the nerves he felt inside during the crucial moments of his event.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth Games\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"demeanour\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"the nerves\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the crucial moments\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"his event\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'At that moment, everyone says I seemed very calm, but actually, storms were raging inside me,' he said.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"storms\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think my shooting pose represented the Olympic spirit very well: the fair play, simplicity, clarity and naturalness.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my shooting pose\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the fair play\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"simplicity\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"naturalness\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why it got so much attention.'\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much attention\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The retired non-commissioned officer in Turkey's gendarmerie also elaborated on his lack of eye equipment.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9729681477658512, \"rank\": 0.02777787583810328, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The retired non-commissioned officer\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"his lack\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"eye equipment\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I never needed that equipment,' he told Turkish outlet Haber Turk.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\", \"score\": 0.8235093490621684, \"rank\": 0.16041640193130366, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tur